Class LiquidDrop

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.image.ImageView
        • gameEngine.Actor
          • game.LiquidDrop
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class LiquidDrop
extends Actor
    A LiquidDrop is an Actor that is able to be released upon the click of the dropper. Once released, the drop will fall straight down and could possibly fall into the moving beaker depending on the accuracy of the click. If the timing of the click is not accurate, the drop will fall on the ground.
